[06/12/2018 21:20:39] <font color="#ffff00">leche,</font>
[06/12/2018 21:20:40] <font color="#ffff00">pan,</font>
[06/12/2018 21:20:41] <font color="#ffff00">galletas,</font>
[06/12/2018 21:20:42] <font color="#ffff00">helado,</font>
[06/12/2018 21:20:42] <font color="#ffff00">maíz,</font>
[06/12/2018 21:20:43] <font color="#ffff00">y uvas.</font>
